===Am faclair===

Tha am faclair a sgr&igrave;obh Dwelly car m&ograve;r agus tha iomadh dealbhan ann.  Tha e soilleir gus an leughadair gur e obair uabhasach m&ograve;r a bha am faclair a rinn Dwelly.  Anns an r&ograve;imh-r&agrave;dh am faclair sgr&igrave;obh Dwelly gun robh e taingeil do an R&igrave;gh airson a chuideachadh agus bha e taingeil cuideachd do a bhean. 

